name: All The Hidden Quanta - Postcard from Leslie Road, Essendon - Photo-bombing 2022/01/10
description: The "All the Hidden Quanta - Postcard from ..." series using Processing visual arts language, explores the concept that we are surrounded by the unseen (unacknowledged? unrealised?), constantly in flux world of quanta. This project was processed from real time camera captures me photo-bombing the view from our apartment. mp4, 1280x960px, 25fps, 50seconds(please loop), 89.2MB.
